<template>
    <div>
        <div class="article-content" v-html="$t('text')"></div>
    </div>
</template>

<script>
    import {scrollArea} from "../../../util";

    export default {
        props: ["up", "down", "esc"],
        watch: {
            up(up) {
                if(up) {
                    scrollArea(document.getElementById("cmd-results"), -1);
                }
            },
            down(down) {
                if(down) {
                    scrollArea(document.getElementById("cmd-results"), 1);
                }
            },
            esc(esc) {
                if(esc) {
                    this.$store.dispatch("popColumn");
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>

<i18n>
    {
        "en": {
            "text": "<h2>Keyboard Shortcuts and Controls</h2><p>Here is a list of all keys used for Emvi and their most common usage. Note that there are a few exceptions from this.</p> <div class=\"table-wrapper\"> <div class=\"table-content\"> <table> <tbody> <tr> <th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Key</p> </th> <th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Description</p> </th> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Shift + Space</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Opens the command menu.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Arrow Up</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Select the previous result.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Arrow Down</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Select the next result.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Enter</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Run a command, open a result, or menu.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Tab</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Used to show a preview of a search result or to select the next result in a form (like within a multi-line text input for example).</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Shift + Tab</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Select the previous result within a form.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Space</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Toggle a checkbox or radio controls.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Delete</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Remove the selected result. You will be asked to confirm the action.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Escape</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Return to the previous menu or search, clear the input or close the command menu.</p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> </div> <h2>Markdown</h2> <p>The editor supports Markdown to quickly format text. Some commands need to be used in-line, while others (like headlines) need to start in a new paragraph. Here is a list of all support Markdown shortcuts.</p> <div class=\"table-wrapper\"> <div class=\"table-content\"> <table> <tbody> <tr> <th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Shortcut</p> </th> <th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Description</p> </th> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p># Text</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Adds a headline. You can also use ## or ### to add second-level and third-level headlines.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>&gt; Text</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Starts a block quote.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>- Text</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Creates an unordered list.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>1. Text</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Creates an ordered list.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>[ ] Text</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Creates a to-do list. You can also use [x] to mark the first box checked.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>```Code</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Starts a code block.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>---</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Inserts a horizontal rule.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>*Text*</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Italic text.</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>**Text**</p> </td> <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> <p>Bold text.</p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> </div> <h2>Contact and Support</h2> <p>You can either contact us by <a href=\"mailto:support@emvi.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">email</a> or by using the /support command. We&#39;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/emvi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://spectrum.chat/emvi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Spectrum</a>.</p>"
